To buffer sum, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0.
bytes at 0 becomes 10.
bytes at 1 becomes 20.
bytes at 2 becomes 30.
bytes at 3 becomes 40.
Let total be 0.
Let i be 0.
While i is less than 4: total becomes total plus (bytes at i as i32); i becomes i plus 1.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Give buffer sum.
